cards.title: exterminate! exterminate!
cards.effectDescription: Play: For each friendly Mars creature, destroy a non-Mars creature with lower power.

cards.title: hypnobeam
cards.effectDescription: Play: Gain control of an enemy creature.

cards.title: key abduction
cards.effectDescription: Play: Return each Mars creature to its owner’s hand. Then, you may forge a key at +9Aember icon current cost, reduced by 1Aember icon for each card in your hand.

cards.title: mothership support
cards.effectDescription: Play: For each friendly ready Mars creature, deal 2Damage icon to a creature. (You may choose a different creature each time.)

cards.title: nyzyk resonator
cards.effectDescription: For each neighbor Nyzyk Resonator has, your opponent’s keys cost +2Aember icon.

cards.title: orbital bombardment
cards.effectDescription: Play: Reveal any number of Mars cards from your hand. For each card revealed this way, deal 2Damage icon to a creature. (You may choose a different creature each time.)

cards.title: phloxem spike
cards.effectDescription: Play: If there are no friendly creatures in play, destroy each creature not on a flank.

cards.title: red planet ray gun
cards.effectDescription: This creature gains, “After Reap: Choose a creature. Deal 1Damage icon to that creature for each Mars creature in play.”

cards.title: sample collection
cards.effectDescription: Play: Put an enemy creature into your archives for each key your opponent has forged. If any of these creatures leave your archives, they are put into their owner’s hand instead.

cards.title: storm crawler
cards.effectDescription:
Storm Crawler only deals 1Damage icon when fighting.
After an enemy creature reaps, stun it.

cards.title: uxlyx the zookeeper
cards.effectDescription:
Elusive. (The first time this creature is attacked each turn, no damage is dealt.)
Reap: Put an enemy creature into your archives. If that creature leaves your archives, it is put into its owner’s hand instead.

cards.title: zorg
cards.effectDescription:
Zorg enters play stunned.
Before Fight: Stun the creature Zorg fights and each of that creature’s neighbors.

cards.title: brain stem antenna
cards.effectDescription: This creature gains, “After you play a Mars creature, ready this creature and for the remainder of the turn it belongs to house Mars.”

cards.title: custom virus
cards.effectDescription: Omni: Sacrifice Custom Virus. Purge a creature from your hand. Destroy each creature that shares a trait with the purged creature.

cards.title: destructive analysis
cards.effectDescription: Play: Deal 2Damage icon to a creature. You may purge any number of cards from your archives. Deal an additional 2Damage icon to the same creature for each card purged this way.

cards.title: entropic manipulator
cards.effectDescription: Play: Choose a player. You may redistribute the damage on the creatures that player controls among that player’s creatures. (You may cause more damage to a creature than it has power.)

cards.title: extinction
cards.effectDescription: Play: Destroy a creature and each creature that shares a trait with it. Gain 1 chain.

cards.title: grommid
cards.effectDescription:
You cannot play creatures.
After an enemy creature is destroyed fighting Grommid, your opponent loses 1Aember icon.

cards.title: hypnotic command
cards.effectDescription: Play: For each friendly Mars creature, choose an enemy creature to capture 1Aember icon from its own side.

cards.title: incubation chamber
cards.effectDescription:
Omni: Reveal a Mars creature from your hand. If you do, archive it.

Most Martians on the Crucible came out of one of these tanks.

cards.title: invasion portal
cards.effectDescription: Action: Discard cards from the top of your deck until you discard a Mars creature or run out of cards. If you discard a Mars creature this way, put it into your hand.

cards.title: killzord mk. 9001
cards.effectDescription:
This creature gets +2 armor and +2 power.
This creature gains skirmish and, “Fight: Gain 1 chain.”

cards.title: martian generosity
cards.effectDescription:
Play: Lose all of your Aember icon. Draw 2 cards for each Aember icon lost.
“F-f-forgive me; I misspoke! Thirty—no, forty—percent discount!”

cards.title: martian hounds
cards.effectDescription:
Play: Choose a creature. For each damaged creature, give the chosen creature two +1 power counters.
Who let the... dogs?... out?

cards.title: qyxxlyx plague master
cards.effectDescription: After Fight/After Reap: Deal 3Damage icon to each Human creature. This damage cannot be prevented by armor.

cards.title: shard of hate
cards.effectDescription:
Action: Stun an enemy creature for each friendly Shard.
Forged from fear.

cards.title: shatter storm
cards.effectDescription:
Play: Lose all your Aember icon. Then, your opponent loses triple the amount of Aember icon you lost this way.
“It’s working!”

cards.title: sniffer
cards.effectDescription:
Action: For the remainder of the turn, each creature loses elusive.
Even the Martians’ pets have a bone to pick with the other lifeforms on the Crucible.

cards.title: total recall
cards.effectDescription: Play: For each friendly ready creature, gain 1Aember icon. Return each friendly creature to your hand.

cards.title: yxlyx stimrager
cards.effectDescription: After Fight: Deal 2Damage icon to a creature and move it to either flank of its controller’s battleline.

cards.title: yzphyz knowdrone
cards.effectDescription: Play: Archive a card. You may purge an archived card to stun a creature.

cards.title: “lion” bautrem
cards.effectDescription:
Deploy. (This creature can enter play anywhere in your battleline.)
“Lion” Bautrem’s neighbors get +2 power.

cards.title: abond the armorsmith
cards.effectDescription:
Other friendly creatures get +1 armor.
Action: For the remainder of the turn, other friendly creatures get +1 armor.

cards.title: aubade the grim
cards.effectDescription:
Play: Capture 3Aember icon.
Reap: Discard 1Aember icon from Aubade the Grim.
